Description

Represents a type of platform that falls down when a player steps on it

This class includes the instructions to how to play the game

This class represents a lazer that can kill characters if being touched.

Menu
This class represents the menu screen where the player can choose what level to play

This class represents a monster that is of person type that can kill a player.

This class represents any person (player or monster) that appears in the game.

Represents a platform that a person can step on and jump on
Player
A player is a person that can take keys.

This class represents a general screen that can appear on the drawing surface
ScreenSwitcher
An interface that represents certain screens with specific numbers that are used in other classes
Spikes
A platform type that represents a set of spikes that characters can't step on, otherwise they 'die'.
Teleporter
This class represents a special type of monster that does not act like a person and teleports around trying to kill the player.
Wall
A kind of platform that is a wall and the player can't walk through it.
